mattlopane 


			2017-06-27T11:23:00+00:00		



Akoustis is a high-tech semiconductor company located in the piedmont technology corridor between Charlotte and Raleigh NC. Corporate headquarters are in Huntersville, NC where it houses administration, sales, engineering and operations.



Akoustis owns and operates a 120,000 sq. ft. commercial wafer manufacturing facility located in Canandaigua, NY, which includes a state-of-the-art class 100/class 1000 cleanroom facility tooled for 150-mm diameter wafer manufacturing






 
   

 


