Company Profile
Sector: Technology
Industry: Hardware
Sub-Industry: Consumer Electronics
Akoustis Technologies, Inc. designs, develops and manufactures radio frequency (RF) filters. The Company uses single-crystal piezoelectric materials to create bulk acoustic wave (BAW) filters for mobile smartphones and other mobile wireless devices.




