			Company Description 


			Akoustis Technologies, Inc. operates in the telecommunications and fiber optics sector. It commercializes and manufactures its patent-pending Bulk One acoustic wave technology to improve the efficiency and signal quality of mobile wireless devices and enabling the internet of things. The company was...
		


                Akoustis Technologies, Inc. operates in the telecommunications and fiber optics sector. It commercializes and manufactures its patent-pending Bulk One acoustic wave technology to improve the efficiency and signal quality of mobile wireless devices and enabling the internet of things. The company was founded in 2014 and is headquartered in Huntersville, NC.
            




